MPV-info: Welcome to the website of the Cavalier King Charles Spaniel kennel "ShineLine". We are a small cozy kennel located in Belarus, the city of Minsk.
DI-info: The Cavalier King Charles Spaniel is a cheerful, shaggy fidget with a pronounced, flirtatious appearance and good-natured character. Enliven the presence of each home and perfectly cope with the role of a reliable companion.
